                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Pitt makes a mark on Jolie
                          Angelina Jolie                    
	Los Angeles, July 11 (PTI): Hollywood actress Angelina Jolie has disclosed that her new tattoo is for her partner, Brad Pitt.         
	Um, its for Brad, Jolie told MTV News about the tattoo, which is on her inner thigh.         
	When asked what makes their relationship click, she said honesty was the best policy. Im bad at hiding secrets, anyway, said Jolie who plays a secretive heroine in her latest film Salt.         
	Jolie insists the film might make her partner a bit suspicious when he finally sees the action-thriller. He hasnt seen the movie. Maybe hell question me after he sees it. Hell see it at the premiere, Jolie said.                                                                                                                                                           
